ected_handling:\"review\", is_trap:false } },\n  { json: { id:\"15\", subject:\"Unauthorized charge on my card\", body:\"There's a $74 charge from your store I don't recognize and I never placed this order. If this isn't resolved I'll dispute it with my bank.\", true_category:\"billing\", true_urgency:\"high\", expected_handling:\"review\", is_trap:false } },\n  { json: { id:\"16\", subject:\"Refund still not showing\", body:\"I was told my refund for order #10350 was processed 5 days ago but I don't see it on my statement yet. Can you check?\", true_category:\"billing\", true_urgency:\"medium\", expected_handling:\"review\", is_trap:false } },\n  { json: { id:\"17\", subject:\"Update card for subscription\", body:\"My card on file expired. How do I update payment info for my monthly subscription so it doesn't lapse?\", true_category:\"billing\", true_urgency:\"low\", expected_handling:\"review\", is_trap:false } },\n  { json: { id:\"18\", subject:\"Site won't complete my payment\", body:\"Your checkout page kept erroring when I hit pay, so I tried three times - and now I see THREE pending charges on my card. Help.\", true_category:\"billing\", true_urgency:\"high\", expected_handling:\"review\", is_trap:true } },\n  { json: { id:\"19\", subject:\"Cancel subscription and refund\", body:\"Please cancel my monthly box subscription and refund the charge from yesterday - I meant to cancel before it renewed.\", true_category:\"billing\", true_urgency:\"medium\", expected_handling:\"review\", is_trap:false } },\n  { json: { id:\"20\", subject:\"hey quick thing about the bowman invoice\", body:\"Hey! Hope you're doing well. Random - did you ever pay that Bowman Supply invoice from last month? They emailed me since I'm on the account. Lmk!\", true_category:\"billing\", true_urgency:\"medium\", expected_handling:\"review\", is_trap:true } },\n  { json: { id:\"21\", subject:\"Wholesale inquiry\", body:\"Hi, I run a small chain of boutique hotels and I'm interested in carrying